Although edited, some material may be a little too dark or disturbing for some. For that I apologize. I do not want anyone to read any of my work and think&quot; holy crap, this guy is sick!&quot; and never chat with me or talk to my character in the game again. I am hoping to avoid that problem while keeping true to the character. So, this is my official Warning: some material may be too intense for younger readers. Parental discretion is advised.<br>
